=============================================================================

Dependencies:
 - SDL
 - libpng

Supported operating systems:
 - Linux
 - Windows(r)
 - OSX and *bsd ports should be a trivial matter

Building:
 $ ./configure && make

Where to get the data:
 These are direct rips from desert strike, so don't download if you don't
 have relevant rights. Take the data dir from:
   www.scaramanga.co.uk/punani-strike-alpha.zip

Patches:
 Yes please

kthxbye
